# Group Authors

## Author List [/v2/authors{?keywords,sort,offset,limit}]
A list contains information of the selected authors

### Get a list of authors [GET]

+ Parameters
    + keywords: `小明` (optional) - Keywords of the names of authors for searching
    + sort: `-updated_at` (optional) - Field to sort by
        + Default: `-updated_at`
        + Members
          + `updated_at` - Sort by updated_at ascending
          + `-updated_at` - Sort by updated_at descending
    + offset: `0` (integer, optional) - The number of authors to skip
        + Default: `0`
    + limit: `10` (integer, optional) - The maximum number of authors to return at a time
        + Default: `10`

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + status: success (required)
        + data (required)
            + meta(meta, fixed-type, required)
            + records (array[Author], fixed-type, required)

+ Response 204

+ Response 500 (application/json)

    + Attributes
        + status: error (required)
        + message: Unexpected error. (required)

+ Response 504 (application/json)

    + Attributes
        + status: error (required)
        + message: Query upstream server timeout. (required)

